Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.75,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.00,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}變得像樣多了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.66,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他們在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.91,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.62,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是新來的那些人的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:44.75,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是什麼聲音？
